ctivation taking place in the context of "work" and traces possible ways of resistance.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Okt 2018) 4aArbeit. 4aArbeiterbewegung. 4aArbeits- und Industriesoziologie. 4aArbeitskraftunternehmer. 4aArbeitssoziologie. 4aEmployee Entrepreneur. 4aGouvernementalität. 4aGovernmentality. 4aIch AG. 4aMachtmechanismen. 4aMachttechnologien. 4aMe Inc.,Entrepreneurial Self. 4aMechanisms of Power. 4aMichel Foucault. 4aSocial Relations. 4aSociological Theory. 4aSociology of Work and Industry. 4aSociology of Work. 4aSociology. 4aSozialität. 4aSoziologie. 4aSoziologische Theorie. 4aSubjectivation. 4aSubjektivierung. 4aTechnologies of Power. 4aUnternehmerisches Selbst. 4aWork. 4aWorking Class Movement.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2018z9783110603231oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.14361/9783839445365zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783839445365.jpg  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb2018